      {
        "question": "Are results precise to the second?",
        "answer": "The tool operates in minutes and hours. It is intended for scheduling-level precision. For sub-minute synchronization (e.g., systems requiring precise timestamps) follow IEEE Precision Time Protocol (PTP) guidance and NIST time sources."
